description:
Are you so accustomed to tragedy and disaster that you’re blind to the signs of the end times? Do you feel a personal sense of urgency for fulfilling Christ’s commission? In this episode, Pastor Pavel Goia looks at the reasons why people lose their sense of urgency and what to do about it. He also discusses why many will not see the signs of Christ’s imminent return even when they’re obvious.

What are the signs you may be insensitive to the Holy Spirit? How can you tell if your heart is in the right place? Learn the type of prayer that will prepare you to meet the greatest crisis of history.
